{"tid":467691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全班第一名刺死導師　對要害連捅數刀","createTime":"2017-11-13T17:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T16:18:52.000Z","uid":56533,"like":163,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"1a17461bae53377aab0fec14cff1dc314e3e5351","tid":467691,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171113/640_754cce3d41955f7457c9d634c88a49c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171113%2F640_754cce3d41955f7457c9d634c88a49c1.jpg&h=e7c02bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國湖南益陽市昨天下午發生一起高三生殺死班導師的命案，只是因為導師鮑方要求學生們留在學校寫東西，但班上第一名的羅宇杰不願意，導師便嗆他不寫就轉班，羅生便拿出一把彈簧刀向導師要害連捅數刀，鮑師送醫後不治。<br />\n<br />\n據《封面新聞》報導，鮑方曾獲評為當地優秀教師，並沒有特別嚴格，他的女兒也在自己擔任班導的班級裡，和兇手是同班同學。而行兇的16歲羅宇杰則是班上第一名，全年級也排在前十名，同學表示，「平時所有老師都對他很好，畢竟他是第一名，老師們都挺喜歡他。」同學說羅生平時看起來很老實，沒想到竟然會行兇。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171113/1240539/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171113%2F1240539%2F&d=RPK1G0yWOc9aoPi5Txb6Zozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=48cf9dc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171113%2F1240539%2F&h=3f255bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171113/1240539/</a>"},{"pid":"6f33988e00ceac13fecfd4e5ddf2e1f1e1502919","tid":467691,"uid":31219,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"隨身帶刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02db7b58fefbcdc2e1e985b32da39625c8158acd","tid":467691,"uid":47645,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨身帶刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶都唔係呢d情況用。。"},{"pid":"a8ed9